import { Div } from "./styles"

export default function Form(){
    return (
        <>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Insert a Sentence"/>
            <select>
                <option>English</option>
                <option>Portuese</option>
                <option>Spanish</option>
                <option>Mandarin</option>
            </select>
            <button>Check</button>
        </>
    )
}
